15.
Further Information on Data Protection
At Shawarmer, we are committed to implementing the requirements of the Personal Data Protection Law in Saudi Arabia to ensure the protection of your personal data and its confidentiality.
Data We Collect
We collect the following information: name, phone number, address, and payment information. This data is necessary to provide our services, such as processing orders, delivery, and customer service.
Data Usage
Your personal data is used solely for the purposes outlined in the privacy policy, such as processing orders, delivery, customer support, and marketing. Your data will not be used for any other purpose without your explicit consent.
Data Retention
We retain your personal data for the necessary period to achieve the purposes for which it was collected. You have the right to request the deletion of your data at any time through the app, and your request will be processed in accordance with applicable laws.
Security and Encryption
We use modern encryption technologies to protect your personal data, both when stored and during transmission. The data is stored on servers, with a level of protection that complies with local and international legal requirements.
Breach Notification
In the event of any breach or unauthorized access to your personal data, we will promptly notify the relevant authorities and affected customers in accordance with the law.